      "name": "OPEN_SR_cell_cost_and_H_cardinality",
      "statement": "(1) Bound SR-cell (Type S first-match) at e\u00b7p using through-pack per r_* / peel structure.\n(2) Prove |H_A_SP| \u2264 2170, or adopt matching-supported A_SP with a residual pair cell for non-M sides.",
      "status": "OPEN"
